{"tid":2350643,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳凱泳首隔離一個獎都冇？","createTime":"2021-01-02T13:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T14:33:42.000Z","uid":366509,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8ba658734f57b8bab6addb80725dbc7c6298d9","tid":2350643,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"林家謙都叫有獎<br />\n<br />\n但隔離咁hit 上晒各大音樂app排行都冇獎？<br />\n<br />\n但零分又有十大<br />\n<br />\n零分spotify排名好尾不過都好hit都有十大但隔離係長期排頭5就冇？<br />\n<br />\n應否杯葛叱吒?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2012年鄧紫棋杯葛叱吒風波\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F2012%E5%B9%B4%E9%84%A7%E7%B4%AB%E6%A3%8B%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E5%8F%B1%E5%90%92%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb0%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=c9723812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2012年鄧紫棋杯葛叱吒風波</a><br />\n<br />\nGEM真係行得太前<br />\n佢唔係香港發展真係好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492a7f0a39fee9c3de3cc020550dee81d56a3d5e","tid":2350643,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"側田：「現在是『下載率』的年代，有誰會開radio或者看電視來聽音樂？司機和老人家吧。MOOV, KKBOX, iTunes等，做個十大吧，最公平確實。<br />\n<br />\n講真最近十年哪一首十大是真的『金曲』，但其實一首歌沒獎不代表不好，命硬=0獎，但現在唱還感動。<br />\n<br />\n我們做singer能打動到，改善到，感染到，就是成功了」他繼續說：「有位前輩跟我說過，這一行會帶到你很高和很低，但是keeping making good music and enjoy , u will be fine. 加油妹妹，Your music is good and u r so young !!」<br />\n<br />\n側田講得好好<br />\n好似得番我地會認真睇個圍威喂show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de78cb141d831cf6f74e5d3054982884f664fbd5","tid":2350643,"uid":366509,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"492a7f0a39fee9c3de3cc020550dee81d56a3d5e","tid":2350643,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"側田：「現在是『下載率』的年代，有誰會開radio或者看電視來聽音樂？司機和老人家吧。MOOV, KKBOX, iTunes等，做個十大吧，最公平確實。<br />\n<br />\n講真最近十年哪一首十大是真的『金曲』，但其實一首歌沒獎不代表不好，命硬=0獎，但現在唱還感動。<br />\n<br />\n我們做singer能打動到，改善到，感染到，就是成功了」他繼續說：「有位前輩跟我說過，這一行會帶到你很高和很低，但是keeping making good music and enjoy , u will be fine. 加油妹妹，Your music is good and u r so young !!」<br />\n<br />\n側田講得好好<br />\n好似得番我地會認真睇個圍威喂show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"所以我哋作為觀眾都好有問題係應該要反省，唔應該係討論最喜愛係邊個拎，依家係個制度有問題，大家會杯葛tvb但唔會杯葛903。<br />\n<br />\n應該用串流音樂排行嚟作準，或者至少加埋入去計算。<br />\n<br />\n2021了仲玩小圈子，又唔係音樂人/拎過獎/有地位嘅人互評，奧斯卡咁。<br />\n<br />\n暫時最好係學韓國，計串流音樂。"},{"pid":"9bf9d68b1a3e221c6626e8588156ccad7098b5bd","tid":2350643,"uid":46018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f8b8896501b6f255e6068b0036a1eaf2aa6666","tid":2350643,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bf9d68b1a3e221c6626e8588156ccad7098b5bd","tid":2350643,"uid":46018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁有屌好過習慣左嘅，學韓國搞掂。<br />\n真正搞爛樂壇明明就係呢啲老屎忽，GEM都走埋啦。"},{"pid":"b21cb3c5416fbd681f826947c0047242ab7e3b8d","tid":2350643,"uid":46018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"75f8b8896501b6f255e6068b0036a1eaf2aa6666","tid":2350643,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bf9d68b1a3e221c6626e8588156ccad7098b5bd","tid":2350643,"uid":46018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁有屌好過習慣左嘅，學韓國搞掂。<br />\n真正搞爛樂壇明明就係呢啲老屎忽，GEM都走埋啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"903個生態係DJ小圈子扮大台<br />\n新城年年比人笑派獎,903最識就包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{